---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import BoardEvolver from "../components/BoardEvolver.tsx";
---

<Layout
  title="Board Evolver: Generate a High Scoring Word Hunt Board"
  description="Use a genetic algorithm to evolve a high scoring Word Hunt board from scratch, then open it straight in the solver to practice."
  path="/evolver"
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 pt-10 pb-6 text-center sm:pt-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold leading-tight text-headline dark:text-headline-dark sm:text-4xl">
      Board Evolver
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-center text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">
      The board evolver uses a genetic algorithm to evolve a high scoring Word Hunt board from scratch.
      Each generation keeps the best scoring boards and mixes them together, so the score climbs over time.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-6">
    <BoardEvolver client:load />
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-10">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">How the Board Evolver Works</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-center text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">
      A genetic algorithm starts with a batch of random boards, scores each one using the same solving
      engine as the main solver, then keeps the highest scoring boards and combines them to create the
      next generation. Repeating this over many generations gradually produces boards packed with valid
      words.
    </p>
    <ul class="mt-6 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2">
      {[
        "Population Size: how many boards are tested per generation, higher is slower but more thorough",
        "Mutation Rate: how often a random letter is swapped in, keeps the search from getting stuck",
        "Interval: how many milliseconds between generations while running",
        "Extreme Mode: occasionally applies a bigger mutation to boost diversity and avoid plateaus",
      ].map((tip) => (
        <li class="card flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-0.5 flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-headline/10 text-xs font-bold text-headline dark:text-headline-dark">✓</span>
          <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">{tip}</span>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-10">
    <div class="card-cta flex flex-col items-center gap-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Start Evolving Your Word Hunt Board</h2>
      <p class="max-w-2xl text-brand-600">
        Want to practice on tougher boards instead of easy ones? Evolve a high scoring board here, then
        send it straight to the solver to study every word it holds.
      </p>
      <a href="/" class="btn-cta">Try the Word Hunt Solver</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
